  "format": "The mid-year sequel to January's auction: Chris Ryan comes in and he, Sean, and Amanda each spend $1,000 on a five-film slate of unreleased second-half-2024 movies. Category triggers (box office, Oscar nominations, an 85 Metacritic score) and a no-more-than-two-sequels rule box everyone in, and Amanda drafts fresh off announcing her pregnancy and coming leave.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "kind": "auction",
      "heading": "The paddles",
      "saleLabel": "Mid-year sale · 2024",
